# TypeScript API rules

- `process` / `processBatch` → single Worker, serial queue
- `info` / `infoBatch` → main thread (WASM header read)
- Batch merge: `{ ...defaults, ...item.options }`; `crop` whole-object override
- Runtime adapter: `web` default, `mp-weixin` + required `wasmPath`
- Do not expose Worker internals or raw wasm init to users
